title: Was the child born alive in 23 weeks "tossed in garbage "?
subtitle: The 2006 Florida case was highlighted by life-support commentators in Sechloria Williams in September 2019.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In 2006, the owner of the abortion clinic cut off the cord of a child born alive before "throwing it" into a biologically dangerous bag and placed its remains in the garbage.
